{"tid":2311610,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中方批評加拿大對趙立堅帖文無端指責 表示強烈不滿 奉勸加拿大不要被傲慢與偏見蒙蔽雙眼","createTime":"2020-12-04T08:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T12:40:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc7a49fd56b1104b76535a9441be0c352e6b909","tid":2311610,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"加拿大外長發言人早前就中國外交部發言人趙立堅有關澳洲軍人殺害阿富汗平民的帖文發表聲明，批評中方發布虛假圖片和信息、有關做法不符合外交行為標準。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐加拿大使館批評是無端指責，中方對此表示強烈不滿和嚴厲譴責。發言人說，加方慣於打著「民主、人權、自由」的旗號，攻擊抹黑他人、干涉別國內政，但對澳洲軍人在阿富汗的殘暴罪行視而不見，甚至還對中方譴責罪行的做法進行無端指責，再次暴露了加方傲慢、偽善和雙重標準的醜惡嘴臉，令人不齒。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，中方奉勸加拿大站在人性良知一邊，站在公道正義的一邊，不要被傲慢與偏見蒙蔽雙眼，不要跟國際上某些勢力同流合污，否則只能自毀形象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563578-20201204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563578-20201204.htm&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=d3403129\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563578-20201204.htm&h=3ddc27fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563578-20201204.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fade7546bb76b7c3a9fe960e130caaa1380f9a2b","tid":2311610,"uid":76804,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfMZRaK.gif&amp;h=1971ccae&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"112d14a13d6f0bacf7fc671ec83582c709e4ae08","tid":2311610,"uid":310275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cea5f6902fadea2ccd45f25ce5e70ce2461b36a","tid":2311610,"uid":27122,"l